metadata.name: untapped power inside
metadata.description:
"Very often we live our normal lives without even noticing that we are busy doing completely the wrong thing. We chase after what we have been indoctrinated in advertising or TV, after trivialities, after trendy clothes that can only spoil you. Life tells you the signs, but we don't see them. In you sits a huge Beast - your potential, your power and true strength, your mission, which is waiting to be released. Relax and trust this inner energy. Don't be afraid of it, at first it will make a mess, but then it will take you like a child by the hands and lead you on your right road. When you let it out, it will exalt you to your highest point. So, ready?......"

5712px x 4429px (300dpi) of pure creativity
